Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:16.69,Typeset,,0,0,0,,Memories
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like the kind of place people would live...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like any kind of factory, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a bunch of black slabs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weird place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But that stuff is the weirdest thing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean this device?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you brought it with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured we could use it for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not gonna use it for anything, jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:03:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean the drawers on the side of the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Most are sealed up tight and inaccessible...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there are ones that are empty...\Nwere they empty to start with
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,or did someone take what was inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when there's something inside, it's not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, huh. All we've found so far is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...the weird device just now,\Nan empty shell, a scrap of cloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...and a button.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all, it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought everything with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured we could use them for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not gonna use them for anything, jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I really thought we could use them\Nfor something or other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What're we gonna use a scrap of cloth for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All these useless, seemingly worthless things\Nare stored away as if they're important...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A mysterious statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi, gimme the camera, the camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure like those.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They're shaped real nice,\Nand they're kinda relaxing to look at!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Cameras are so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never forget the things you took pictures of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank Kanazawa for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was Kanazawa again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. He was the guy who gave us the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've forgotten about him without the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally you wouldn't forget\Nthat sorta thing that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he's doing well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we have this camera,\Nwe'll never forget him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking about him as if he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But no matter if he's dead or alive,\Nwe're probably not gonna run into him again, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Or Ishii, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it'd be difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then one day we'll probably forget about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't see it because it was so small,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but every drawer has a name written on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet that's the person who owned what was inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So the stuff inside was forgotten by those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think they were forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They put them in here so they wouldn't be forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,These are graves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Graves...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet they left behind these names\Nand the things they owned
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so someone would see it and remember them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But now there isn't anyone\Npassing through like we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and everyone in the world is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so who would remember them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well look, they've got this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what that statue's here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's snowing harder, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna get colder again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta put them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Put what back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The stuff you took with you, Yuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll lose all their meaning if they leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we know where they all go...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Does this go here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they're all the same in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:40.80,Typeset,,0,0,0,,Spiral
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That scared me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,An old beam fell down...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this scaffolding gonna hold up...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine, it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You always say it's gonna be fine, Yuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There might be danger lurking ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything seems so dangerous that I actually\Nstart thinking that everything'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The elevator on the outside\Nof the tower was broken down...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a good thing this path was here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This tower's way thinner than\Nthe last one we came up, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a different type of tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I like going up this way better than riding an elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so done with dangling by a rope like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we haven't even made it to the higher level yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Around, and around...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:11:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we really going up, or are we going down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, we're going up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're going around and\Naround the same location,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it really makes you miss our usual, unchanging days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's hurry and get to the top\Nso we can go back to those usual days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but the more we move,\Nthe more danger we'll be in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are quick to turn into a coward\Nwhen you're up high, Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you live if you're afraid of dying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a good line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How long does this path go on for...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My head's starting to spin, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A spinning spiral...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My head's spinning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:25.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,Chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:28.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,Chi, stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The path...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, look there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That the exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's another way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone must've made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd they make it on the outside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like it'd be a problem\Nfor people to use, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I hate going up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi, how can you live if-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it, you don't have to say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi, hit the accelerator!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Never thought I'd be this happy\Nto see this path again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the entrance to the next level!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're on the next level up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back to our usual flat path.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it sure is dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We sleep, wake up, eat, and move...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,then sleep again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When you think about it,\Nour lives go around and around, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That means life is just a spiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will we end up when we\Nreach the end of the spiral?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:05.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,Moonlight
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nights where you can see the Moon\Nreally get you pumped up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here we can use...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets you pumped up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always in such a bad mood, Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really in a bad mood, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this seriously and look for stuff, Yuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, found a nice stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I feel a stranger power in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be the Moon's magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic power, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought there'd be something here\Nsince there were lots of houses still standing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is falling apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The moonlight's shining in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Moonlight power at 100%!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,Moonlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Moonlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:13.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,Moonlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Moonlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, could you calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,Moonlight! Moonlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop picking up sticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Glass containers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Some have stuff inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's got stuff inside, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's three altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's inside them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's written here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It says...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"B... Beeu", I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The top's on real tight, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Opened it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's golden water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kinda sparkly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't we have a glass container with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:19:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks almost like the moonlight's melting into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kinda bitter... but kinda sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so fizzy and weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's open another!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu, think first...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:03.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi's gone crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face is really stretchy, Yuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the power of the Moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the moonlight really did melt into that water!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The light of the Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, let's go really really high up...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...and go to the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good. The Moon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder what it's like up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chi! Don't eat my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My head hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
